Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums

Crosby, Stills & Nash opened

reviews.review_text: 1st show this new upload/recording is tremendous! Listened to this show yesterday for the 1st time in about 10yrs. Amazing separation with Phil's bass LOUD and the perfect mix of crowd in there too. Only show of the @35-40 I saw that I ever listen to. Amazing energetic performance and setlist. Summer 90 was great! Have to think a box set with videos/DVDs of some combo of shows from 7/4-7/16/90 will be released eventually.
